          <span class="accordion-item__title"
          >
            Experience, up to a maximum of 35 points
          </span>
          
            
              
                
                
              
            
          
        </button>
      </h4>
      
        
          <p class=""> </p><p class="">Experience is assessed from the five years before applying for a permanent resident visa (signing your application) until the decision on your application is made. You can earn a starting point of 20 for 2 years of relevant experience.</p>
        
      

      
        
      

    </li>
  
    <li class="accordion-item">

      
        
      

      <h4 aria-level="3" role="heading" class="
          accordion-item__title-wrapper
          
          
          
